Getting started
Creating a club — tap "Create club" on the welcome screen, give it a name, and share the invite code with your group.
Joining a club — tap "Join club" and enter the invite code from your club admin.
Adding a bet — tap the camera button to photograph a bet slip (we'll read the details automatically) or use "Enter manually".
FAQs
Can I be in multiple clubs? Yes — tap your club name at the top of the screen to switch between clubs.
What's a bonus bet? When adding a bet, select "Bonus bet" if the stake came from a bookmaker promotion rather than your own money. P&L is calculated accordingly (no stake returned on a win).
What's a club bet? A bet attributed to the club as a whole rather than an individual member — useful for syndicate bets.
How do I leave a club? Long-press your name in the Club tab and select "Leave club". Your bets remain in the club history.
I'm not receiving notifications — check that notifications are enabled for Puntly in your iPhone Settings → Notifications.
